		font-size: 25px;
		font-weight: 800;
	}
	button{
		background-color: #598BCF;
		border: 2px solid #2A70B9;
		margin-left: 30px;
		border-radius: 5px;
		width: 90px;
		height: 45px;
		color: #fff;
		font-family:  Microsoft JhengHei;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 25px;
		position: relative;
		vertical-align: middle;
		cursor: pointer;
	}
	input{
		margin-left: 30px;
		width: 320px;
		height: 45px;
		border-radius: 5px;
		border:2px solid #ccc;
		position: relative;
		vertical-align: middle;
		font-size:25px; 
